Dear Sir/Madam,<br />
<br />
Greetings from Aditya Birla Sun Life Insurance Company Limited.<br />
<br />
We wish to inform you that your Group Policy is due for renewal on the above-mentioned date.<br />
<br />
We request you to share member data 30 days in-advance of the Renewal date in the attached format for us to compute renewal premium. Renewal process for your Policy should be completed on or before renewal date to ensure uninterrupted coverage of your members.<br />
<br />
We would require the following documents to renew your above policy:<br />
• Complete Renewal Premium (inclusive of Goods and Services Tax)<br />
• Renewal quote – dated &amp; signed by your Authorized Signatory<br />
• Normal Retirement Age (NRA) Extension Letter for any members above the NRA age<br />
• Details of your expatriate members (Location &amp; Country of posting, duration of stay)<br />
• Cancelled cheque copy of the Policyholder<br />
<br />
Please be informed that no grace period is available for the above policy.<br />
<br />
The policy will be renewed only on completion of all the above requirements. In the event of non- compliance of all the requirements on or prior to the renewal date, the policy will lapse with effect from the renewal date.<br />
<br />
Post renewal of the policy, kindly ensure that the member data is updated with us regularly. We also recommend that you remit a buffer deposit in addition to your renewal premium towards meeting your monthly member additions/enhancements requests.<br />
<br />
Please quote your captioned Policy Number in all your communications with us.<br />
<br />
In case you need any clarifications, please do not hesitate to contact us at absli.grouphelpline@adityabirlacapital.com<br />
<br />
Best Regards,<br />
Group Business Operations &amp; Services<br />
Aditya Birla Sun Life Insurance Company Limited.<br />
Email us at: absli.grouphelpline@adityabirlacapital.com</p>
